  "where_it_fits": "Accessed from a Client Detail page within the Institution \u2192 Clients flow (and reachable via product/account shortcuts in the left sidebar), this module is part of the Products/Accounts area showing FD and RD accounts for individual clients. It integrates with product configuration (deposit products and interest rate charts) and appears alongside other account detail pages with tabs for Summary, Transactions, and Charges.",
